snippet.textDisplay:
If you want to try something different with liquid smoke, try my smoked salmon spread.its good on crackers or the small cocktail bread
1 can salmon....bones removed
6 oz. Room temperature cream cheese (more or less to taste)
1 Tbsp horseradish
1/8 tsp liquid smoke
Dash or 2 of garlic powder

Mix together and let sit overnight in refrigerator then enjoy!

snippet.textDisplay: One thing you may have missed on the Avocado Mayo is that it wont break down so fast on a heated item, like toast,  you put regular mayo on toast and it turns to oil, the avocado mayo will  not break down and holds up great to heat, so it should shine on sushis with grilled mayo on top and other heated mayo dishes.

snippet.textDisplay: I typically roll with & understand the different food terms the Brits use for things I'm familiar with under another name, but today did take me by surprise when I heard "egg mayo" and it took me like a solid 30 seconds before I realized that's what they call "egg salad." I went through almost the exact same thing when they did "chicken salad" and it was just a salad with chicken, so I don't know why it took me by surprise here with this.
